snippet: A hunger strike over prison conditions in July ended following negotiations, but inmates who resumed the strike last week are showing little inclination to compromise.
lead_paragraph: A hunger strike over prison conditions in July ended following negotiations, but inmates who resumed the strike last week are showing little inclination to compromise.
